be se kɛ. ‘Ɔ kwlá kɔman lika uflɛ m’ɔ loman wunmiɛn’n. Ɔ fata kɛ ɔ lafi. Ɔ ti klanman i bo lɔ
be flɛ i kɛ saule. Fluwa kan!’
